  "prompt": "How many seats are available in MA English in GGSIPU?",
  "response": "Guru Gobind Singh Indraprastha University (GGSIPU) in Delhi offers courses in various disciplines, including a Master of Arts (MA) in English. The exact number of seats available for the MA English program can vary from year to year based on university policies and subject to approval from relevant authorities like the University Grants Commission (UGC) and other academic bodies.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information regarding seat availability, you should refer to the official GGSIPU website or contact the university's admissions office directly. They will provide the specific details for the current academic year and any other relevant information.",
